\[
\mathrm{IE}(\mathrm{H}_2) = 4.478 + 13.598 - 2.651
\]

First, add \(4.478\) and \(13.598\):
\[
4.478 + 13.598 = 18.076
\]

Then subtract \(2.651\):
\[
18.076 - 2.651 = 15.425
\]

