- \(B_3\): \(\frac{1}{8} \times 0.5 = 0.0625\)
- \(B_4\): \(\frac{1}{8} \times 0.75 = 0.09375\)

The sum is \(0.5 + 0 + 0.0625 + 0.09375 = 0.65625\), which is rounded to three decimal places to give \(0.656\).

