- Energy for three single bonds: 19.098 kcal/mol
- Energy for three double bonds: 7.884 kcal/mol
- Total energy: 26.982 kcal/mol

Rounded to three significant figures, the total energy is 27.0 kcal/mol, based on the input values having three significant figures (bond lengths: 1.53 Å, 1.335 Å, 1.397 Å; force constants: 500 N/m, 950 N/m).

